  ],
  "remarks": "Ali Reza Khanchi was the head of AEOI’s Tehran Nuclear Research Centre (TNRC) and is a scientist conducting research for the TNRC. The TNRC is involved in experiments on plutonium separation. He continues to cooperate with the Atomic Energy Organisation of Iran (AEOI) as a scientist. Therefore, Khanchi is engaged in and providing support to Iran’s nuclear proliferation activities.",
